Quickstrike:




Seated at the command chair, Quickstrike slouched down some, with a 
surly look on his face. He was supposed to talk to Black Arachnia, 
but she disappeared on him. He supposed she was busy. 

He opened his comm-link to Tarantulas. "Hey, T, didn't happen t' know 
what Black Arachnia wanted did ya?"
